- description: Settle Bevy vs Fyrox and drop the non-chosen frontend to non-blocking
- horizon: near
- status: declared
- notes: ADR-0003 — resolve by end of Envelope.

### Mid Horizon

#### wire-format-settled
- description: Choose the Rust<->Elixir wire format and persistence strategy
- horizon: mid
- status: declared

#### adaptive-security-ai
- description: AI countermeasures that react to hacker interference (Bicycle+)
- horizon: mid
- status: declared

### Far Horizon

#### full-experience
- description: Adaptive security AI, emergent tension, complete multiplayer (Motorcycle)
- horizon: far
- status: declared
